item.title: Episode 01
item.description: WorkplaceDudes S01E01 Episode 01 has been recorded and can be viewed via our Youtube channel. In this episode, we’re talking about Microsoft exams. So how do you go about it, what resources do you use and, in our opinion, the best method to prepare. Since this was the first episode for us, we had to get used to it. So sometimes things do go wrong, but that is a learning process for us.
